column4:
I got to spend time with business owners and workers at 
@VaughnHockey, @CAM_Logic, Apothecary &amp; Co., 24th Street Tavern, @DuttonFarmInc and @LavaMTCoffee on Tuesday.

Their resilience is a testament to the ingenuity and grit that makes American businesses so strong.

